\'93We celebrate the rise of Nationalism and the fall of Antifa,\'94 answers a girl with green streaks in her dark hair.\
\
\'93Yes, before the wave, some misguided people were trying to destroy our country. \'97 Can anyone name a problem we had then?\'94\
